        <h2>Visitor Information</h2>
        <div class="info-cards">
            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>Opening Hours</h3>
                <p>Most temples are open from early morning to late evening. Specific timings may vary, so it's best to check before visiting.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>Best Times to Visit</h3>
                <p>The best time to visit temples is during the cooler months (October to March). Avoid peak summer and monsoon seasons for a comfortable visit.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>Entry Fees</h3>
                <p>Many temples do not charge an entry fee, but some may require a nominal donation. It's advisable to carry some change for donations.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>Traveler Tips</h3>
                <p>Respect local customs and dress codes. Carry a bottle of water and some snacks, especially if the temple is in a remote area.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
